<?xml version="1.0" encoding="iso-8859-1"?> <legaldoc> <law type="statute"> <section id="id4"> <sectno id="id5">Section 1.</sectno><amendatorysection chaptername="Power Districts and Corporations" id="id6" publishedsource="AnnualSupplement" statutenumber="70-2001"><bookinfo>Reissue Revised Statutes of Nebraska</bookinfo><statuteno>70-2001</statuteno><catchline>Legislative findings.</catchline> <para>The Legislature finds that it is in the public interest to:</para> <para>(1) Encourage customer-owned renewable energy resources;</para> <para>(2) Stimulate the economic growth of this state;</para><para>(3) Encourage diversification of the energy resources used in this state; and</para><para>(4) Maintain low-cost, reliable electric service.</para></amendatorysection></section><source><para>Laws 2009, LB436, &#167; 1.</para></source>  </law> </legaldoc>